\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs32 \cf2 Through the DVD, filmgoers can engage in several features that expand or tell something new about the primary movie. What I took away from the special edition of 
\f1 This is Spinal Tap 
\f0 is that by preserving artifice, the film brings a critical self-awareness to the construction of documentary. Using Spinal Tap\'92s commentary and the Di Bergi interview brought the extra touch on the fabrication and ethical concerns on how filmmakers represent themselves and their subjects. To me, I believe if the film had information on \'93the making of\'94 it would undermine the construction that the mock-documentary is \'93real.\'94 I believe by having the actors playing their characters perform a reflexive function, the questions and issues the film wants to bring out are more apparent. 
