\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs32 \cf2 Like the \'93essence\'94 of the show, it was also important for Guest to capture the angst and anticipation for the characters. For Levy, he said he was nervous during his performance in the Mayflower scenes. In the commentary, he compares his feelings in the dog show to the auditions in 
\f1 Guffman
